{"id": 5718, "title": "Ticket #5718: Fix printing ads as xml with whitelist", "description": "<blockquote>\nWhen using a white-list to print parts of <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClassAds\" title=\"Class Ads\">ClassAds</a></span> in XML format, we can't have the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ExprTrees\" title=\"Expr Trees\">ExprTrees</a></span> exist in both the original ad and a new temporary ad. It messes with the parentScope pointers and can cause a crash. We need to copy the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ExprTrees\" title=\"Expr Trees\">ExprTrees</a></span>.\n\n<p>If we're printing the entire ad as XML, then we don't need the temporary ad and no copying is necessary.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2016-Jun-27 15:06:29 by tlmiller:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>Code Review</strong>\n\n<p>Approved.  (NB: The copied <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ExprTree\" title=\"Expr Tree\">ExprTree</a></span> will be deallocated when tmp_ad goes out of scope.)</p></blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Jun-27 16:08</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/cff8a06ad6feed6b4c1406f716834496a23b4ca8\">[48669]</a></span>: Version history for -xml crash fix. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5718\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5718'); return false;\" title=\"Fix printing ads as xml with whitelist\">#5718</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Jun-09 15:13</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/42d06de5ce92b4516086a8d14b50309a43a1fbe8\">[48530]</a></span>: Don't share an <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ExprTree\" title=\"Expr Tree\">ExprTree</a></span> between ads when prining as XML. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5718\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5718'); return false;\" title=\"Fix printing ads as xml with whitelist\">#5718</a></span> Placing a single <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ExprTree\" title=\"Expr Tree\">ExprTree</a></span> in two <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClassAds\" title=\"Class Ads\">ClassAds</a></span> simultaneously messes up the parentScope and causes a crash in some cases. Copy the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ExprTree\" title=\"Expr Tree\">ExprTree</a></span> instead.  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2016-Jun-27 16:08", "status": "resolved", "created": "2016-Jun-09 14:31", "fixed_version": "2016-Jun-09 14:31", "broken_version": "v080400", "priority": "3", "subsystem": "ClassAd", "assigned_to": "jfrey", "derived_from": "", "creator": "jfrey", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "", "due_date": ""}